headline: Global Copper Demand Projected to Outpace Supply by Over 500,000 Tonnes In 2025, Driving Upward Price Pressure
summary: Copper—long hailed as "the metal with a PhD in economics"—has become central to industry, agriculture, infrastructure, and global development. As we look to 2025, the copper price outlook 2025 supply demand forecast takes on increasing importance.
